						<span class="entry-info-prep entry-info-prep-cat-links">Posted in</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/category/survival-preparedness" title="View all posts in Podcasts" rel="category tag">Podcasts</a>					</p>
													<p class="tag-links">
						<span class="entry-info-prep entry-info-prep-tag-links">Tagged</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/tag/bol" rel="tag">BOL</a>, <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/tag/bug-out-location" rel="tag">bug out location</a>, <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/tag/permaculture" rel="tag">permaculture</a>					</p>
