			<div id="post-6235" class="post-6235 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-survival-preparedness tag-bol tag-bov tag-bug-our-vehicle tag-bug-out-location tag-military-vehicles">
			<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-868-wade-bowlin-on-bug-out-vehicles" title="Permalink to Episode-868- Wade Bowlin on Bug Out Vehicles" rel="bookmark">Episode-868- Wade Bowlin on Bug Out Vehicles</a></h2>

			<div class="entry-meta">
				 <span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-868-wade-bowlin-on-bug-out-vehicles" title="10:34 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">March 28, 2012</span></a> <span class="byline"><span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/author/Modern Survival" title="View all posts by Modern Survival">Modern Survival</a></span></span><span class="comments-link"><span class="meta-sep">|</span> <a href="http://www.thesurvivalpodcast.com/episode-868-wade-bowlin-on-bug-out-vehicles#comments" title="Comment on Episode-868- Wade Bowlin on Bug Out Vehicles">52 Comments</a></span>
			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->

