<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.prepperpedia.com/" target="_blank">www.prepperpedia.com</a> &#8211; (Wade&#8217;s Site &#8211; in beta)</li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.govliquidation.com/" target="_blank">GovernmentLiquidation.com </a></li>
<li><a target="_blank" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6eK-1Ld7sJY&amp;sns=em" target="_blank">Wade Doing Things with his Ford Raptor that Should Not be Done</a></li>
