<li>What do you do after opening large freeze dried amounts of food you can&#8217;t use quickly</li>
<li>Why is unemployment higher but more people are now buying houses</li>
<li>A young high school girl SCHOOLS the school!  FRICKEN AWESOME!!</li>
</ul>
